title: Summer Catch Up: Internships, Travels & A Few Laughs
itunes:title: Summer Catch Up: Internships, Travels & A Few Laughs
description: So excited to be back in Athens together! Welcome to our first official podcast episode of Gals on the Go. We totally bummed out for this episode eating Uber Eats in our Nike shorts and t-shirts recapping on our summer travels, internships, and hilarious encounters. We also introduce you to the episode format and how each one will work. It is so fun to be doing this together as best friends. We really hope you guys enjoy our first podcast. Rate us if you enjoyed it and expect a NEW podcast every week. Lots of love, Brooke & Danielle @daniellecarolan @brookemiccio
